Life Line Screening

Life Line Screening

40+ Preventive Health

Fast, painless, non-invasive screenings with nearby appointment options at 14,000+ U.S. locations

Annual Screening Packages for Adults 40+

Take control before symptoms take over.

Check key indicators for stroke risk, heart disease, and chronic illness with a practical screening visit designed for adults 40 and over.

Includes: carotid, PAD, AAA, and atrial fibrillation screening

Packages available for: women 40+, men 40+, and all adults 40+

Practical answers. Minimal disruption.

Nearby screening events make it easier to fit preventive care into a normal routine. Appointments are designed to be quick and comfortable, and results are typically available online in about 10 days.

Trusted proof, clearly stated

Over 10 million customers have turned to Life Line Screening for preventive health insights.

Scheduling is available across 14,000+ U.S. screening locations, helping eligible recipients find appointments near home.

The experience is built to be fast, painless, and non-invasive—so acting on health questions can feel manageable, not overwhelming.

Book a nearby screening with confidence

See available screening events near you and choose the package that fits your age 40+ preventive care needs.

Find a Screening Near You

Life Line Screening exists to make preventive health screening more accessible for adults who want useful information before major symptoms appear. The focus of these annual cardiovascular and chronic disease screening packages is straightforward: help people understand important risk factors in a practical, medically reassuring setting.

The service reflects a simple belief that early detection can support better conversations, better planning, and greater peace of mind. For eligible adults 40+, screening for concerns tied to stroke risk and vascular health offers a proactive step that feels informed rather than alarmist.

Life Line Screening has built its reputation around making this process feel easier to approach—clear packages, convenient locations, and a non-invasive experience that helps preventive care fit into real life.

Thank you for considering a practical step toward clearer health insight.

Life Line Screening  •  Preventive screenings for adults 40+  •  Convenient U.S. screening events

